transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

addController(address).notice: Enables an address to mint / burn

configure(uint256).notice: Allows DAO to update game parameters

mint(uint8,bool).notice: ChainLink VRF request: Mints a new ERC721 token: 90% chefs, 10% rats The first 20% are purchased with native token, the remaining cost $FFOOD

removeController(address).notice: Disables an address from minting / burning

setKitchen(address).notice: Sets the kitchen address to optionally stake newly minted characters in
